<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>이미지 변환기</title>

    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/imgconvertor.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/slider.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/slick/slick-theme.css"/>
	<style>
	</style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./nav') %>
    <%- include('./accordion') %>

    <main>
        <!-- <form action="/convert-image" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data"> -->
          <input type="file" class="upload" accept=".avif, .jpeg, .jpg, .jpe, .tile, .dz, .png, .tiff, .tif, .webp, .gif" id="fileInput" style="display: none" onchange="handleFileSelect()" multiple/>
          <div class="upload-area" onclick="handleClick(event)" ondrop="handleDrop(event)" ondragover="handleDragOver(event)">
            <div class="here">
              <img id="addImg" class="add-img" src="/images/folder-add.svg" />
              <p class="add-txt">클릭 또는 파일을 끌어다 놓으세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="convert_wrap">
            <span>이미지 확장자 변환</span>
            <button class="upload-img-btn" type="button" onclick="handleClick(event)">이미지 업로드</button>
            <!-- <div class="select-convert"> -->
              <select class="format-selector" name="format" required>
                <option value="avif">AVIF</option>
                <option value="jpg" selected>JPG(기본)</option>
                <option value="jpeg">JPEG</option>
                <option value="bmp">BMP</option>
                <option value="gif">GIF</option>
                <option value="png">PNG</option>
                <option value="tiff">TIFF</option>
                <option value="webp">WEBP</option>
              </select>              
              <div class="open-help">
                <span>도움말(클릭)</span>
                <img class="help-icon" src="/images/help.svg">
              </div>
              <button class="convert-all-btn" type="button" onclick="convertAllImage()">변환 후 다운로드</button>
                
            <!-- </div> -->
          </div>

    </main>
    <div class="help-modal">
      <div class="modal-overlay"></div>
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-content-wrapper">
          <img class="close-modal" src="/images/deletebtn.svg">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">사용방법</h1>
          <p>1. <b>"이미지 업로드"</b> 버튼을 클릭하여 변환하고자 하는 이미지를 업로드합니다.</p>
          <p>2. 또는 <b>좌측 영역을 클릭</b>하거나, <b>파일을 끌어다 놓아 줍니다.</b></p>
          <p>3. 변환하고 싶은 확장자를 선택합니다.</p>
          <p>4. <b>"변환 후 다운로드"</b> 버튼을 눌러 업로드한 이미지들을 선택한 확장자로 변환합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- footer -->
    <%- include('./footer') %>

    <script src="/js/img-convert.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/common.js"></script>

    <script></script>
  </body>
</html>
